Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.02,0:00:08.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(40,300)}{\c&HA0A0A0&}This story is fiction. The names of people,\Nplaces and groups are imaginary.\NObey traffic rules and drive safely.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.10,0:00:28.75,MainStyle,,0100,0000,0310,,{\bord0}INITIAL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:30.15,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Information, spreads in a matter of seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:32.45,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...but we don't know how to choose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.45,0:00:34.38,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who say, "Money can't buy my love..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:36.34,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...deserves a lariat three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:38.27,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,We make love according to the manuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:40.24,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't notice the lack of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:42.86,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we suffocate, let's yell. Ho!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:44.00,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,In the midnight dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:47.97,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,No place to relax in the sleepless city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:51.91,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,We smile without dropping our guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:00:56.02,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,It's safe to lie and the truth is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:01:00.07,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Desperately wanna shut and break out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:01.95,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we gotta start.  Let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.69,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move into the brand new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:05.95,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dive into the brand new trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:09.67,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You're afraid of a big world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:11.97,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:13.94,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we go full speed and funky beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:15.67,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll surely shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:17.57,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:18.52,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Trip to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:20.42,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Here we go to an unknown world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:22.17,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a newborn traveler.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:24.22,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Unstable footsteps are fun to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:26.32,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Get things done right, only when needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:27.84,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,So many people in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.84,0:01:30.14,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...sometimes, you'll receive slanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:32.18,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's warp uninteresting things...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:33.67,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...and lead at least a rational life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:35.45,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our law.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:46.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No oncoming traffic.\NLet's show off, Mako!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.53,0:01:47.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:48.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:30.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Im...impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:35.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We knew that the Eight-Six was extraordinary\Nfrom the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:39.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided this race would be the last!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:43.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So unless we try our best,\NI won't be satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:46.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you have gotten so timid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:51.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst!  You're like baggage\Nin the passenger seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:53.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Baggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:56.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're only ballast, worsening\Nthe power to weight ratio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:59.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}She's one of those who changes\Ntheir personality behind the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:01.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,HOW CAN YOU CALL ME BALLAST?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:04.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'VE GOT A NICE BODY, AND I'M NOT\NCHUBBY OR FAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:07.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're a 49 kg handicap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,47 KG!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:13.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've said that,\NI can't stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:20.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, Mako!\NDrive like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's more like it.{what I wanted.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:26.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn hard, as if you were going to hit\Nthe cliff in the next corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:28.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Sayuki.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.26,0:03:58.19,MainStyle,,0070,0000,0347,,{\fade(255,0,248,0,1010,4870,5760)}{\2a&HFF&}Race-Settling Super Drift
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good night, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:02.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:07.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:11.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...when will I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:17.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, since school\Nstarts again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:23.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Natsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:42.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Next corner is sandy, so stay\Non the inner edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:43.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Sayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:00.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No oncoming car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:02.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Drift in the next corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:19.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I was distracted by the car behind me\Nand I couldn't drive at my own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:25.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Somewhere in my mind, I thought\Nno one could keep up with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:30.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}But I realize now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:34.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}There's no way I can drive fast\Nif I watch my rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:38.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I won't look in the mirror again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:40.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Skid here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:55.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be many more corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:06:00.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Takumi is keeping up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:04.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly speaking, I thought\Nthey'd come back right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:05.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:09.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he can't overtake them,\Nhe'll outrun them in the second heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:11.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How could he possibly overtake them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:13.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how he can keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:19.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He chose to be the pursuer on\Na course he's never driven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:31.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}It started!\NGreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:37.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}I'm Sato Mako.\NCall me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:39.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}I'm really sor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:45.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}For my memory of this summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:49.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}...would you let me race against Akina's\NEight-Six on the Usui mountain pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:52.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}That's my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}If you make my wish come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:07:00.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}...you can have my virginity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:09.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:12.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How come you look out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be thinking about Mako.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It shows on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I...I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:25.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:29.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mako is a nice girl.\NI agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:31.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:38.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened, but you should\Ngo after her again after this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:41.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,She's too good to give up on so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Drift here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:30.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A car's coming, but you'll pass it\Nin the third corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so don't worry now\Nand go full throttle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:34.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Sayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:51.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Next one, the car'll appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people are racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:04.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:08.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell how good they are by watching\Nhow they drive the downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:18.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I...incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:27.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:31.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Sayuki never misses oncoming cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:37.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}She never misses the headlights, which reflect\Noff the leaves several corners away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:41.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Grip!  Get close to the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:56.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Great, Mako.\NThis is more like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:01.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Drift all the way and clear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:29.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No oncoming car, so drift!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:42.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Incredible.\NShe's dangerously good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:48.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Skilled Road Racers always keep\Na slight margin of safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:52.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}They appear to be driving at the limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:55.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...but they use the full gripping potential\Nof the tires only at the exits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:11:00.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}They save the tires when braking\Nand at the turn-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:05.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Because one mistake means crashing\Non the street with no escape zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:14.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...she doesn't have that margin right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:19.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Her tension is so high that\Nshe hasn't noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:29.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I wonder if I should tell\Nher about it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:38.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's my role to tell her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:50.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:54.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I shouldn't disturb her while\Nshe's driving so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:57.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:12:02.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}We're the best partners, so I'll\Nbelieve in your skill, Mako.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:06.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}You're driving better than ever before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:25.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Damn, what an entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:28.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}She increased her pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:32.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}If she goes any faster,\NI'll reach my limit first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:38.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Even now, I'm using the\Nfull potential of the tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:41.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Damn, I can't...?
