Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.37,0:14:16.56,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Wings of fire, jyuu ni hateshinaku takaku tobu\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}Wings of fire. We fly high so freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:19.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't outrun him, there'll be\Nno place to settle the race!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.66,0:14:22.03,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Wings of fire, futari wa speed ageteyuku\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}Wings of fire. The two of us pick up speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:20.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:24.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No oncoming car, so take\Nit at your best pace!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.17,0:14:23.03,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Higher.\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}Higher.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.04,0:14:29.42,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Wings of fire, hirogaru kono sora wo kakemeguru\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}Wings of fire. We fly around in the open sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The Eight-Six slowed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:47.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:53.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mako!\NYour entry speed's too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:12.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't recover!\NJust spin to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:16.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, get by!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:06.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We're safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:11.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I admit our total defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:16.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's incredible.\NHe's got much better range.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:28.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm completely satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:32.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I recalled...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:36.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...those exciting feelings from\Nwhen we started racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:50.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We were obsessed with\Ndriving until daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:53.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The pure feeling from those days...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:59.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We crossed the limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:02.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you were wonderful till that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:05.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best driving\NI've ever seen from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:07.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:11.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'll leave it up to you, Mako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:14.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:18.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:24.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no tears.  I'm so happy\Nto have had a great race.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:38.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:51.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I...I wonder how the\Nfirst heat turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:53.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they going to start\Nthe second run?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:02.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:14.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, I can't believe\Nthis myself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:18.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be a second\Nheat, will there, Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:23.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No second run.\NOnce was enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:28.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:36.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't want to see Takumi lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:40.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:43.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,W...what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:45.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:51.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me say\Nthat we lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:52.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He won.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:01.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,MEGCSINÁLTA!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:04.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,MEGCSINÁLTA!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:17.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly speaking, we didn't think we\Ncould lose on our home course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:22.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I just kept following you, so\NI wouldn't get outrun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:25.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I don't think I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:33.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be proud of yourself, because\Nyou have such wonderful skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:35.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:40.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We've driven here so often,\Nwe were very confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:47.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But we couldn't outrun a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:49.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means we lost, right, Mako?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Mako...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:20:00.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a wonderful race.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:15.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:21.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:26.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's totally superior in controlling a car,\Nbut he's so reserved in other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:31.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like this all the time.\NHe acts so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:34.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost like he's always asleep,\Nexcept for driving a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:36.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:38.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:43.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But how can you be\Nso good at your age?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:50.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Why don't you go after her again,\Nafter the race?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:54.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}She's too good to give up on so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:58.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:05.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,T...thanks for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:11.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mako, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:14.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani, don't be depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:17.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Road Racers don't need a girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:27.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,R...right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:35.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,When I look closely, he's got\Nmy favorite kind of cute face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:39.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:41.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiwara Ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:45.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm Takeuchi Itsuki.\NEighteen years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.35,0:21:48.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My sign is Leo, and my blood type is 0.\NMy favorite car is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.63,0:21:51.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I...I'm not asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:22:01.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why don't we go to the\Npool together for friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:03.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good, sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:05.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:08.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll go, right, Takumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:12.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And you of course, Iketani?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.66,0:22:15.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:18.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Sayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.24,0:22:21.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.35,0:22:26.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!\NI'll go in my Eight-Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:43.91,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Ai ni tsukarehate samayotte ta koro}Being tired of love, I wandered around...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.33,0:22:50.65,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Yokubou dake ni kararete miushinatteita}...I lost myself to carnal desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:23:05.63,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Kimagure na unmei wa mujaki na hitomi ni miserate yuku}Innocent eyes slowly charm my unpredictable fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.22,0:23:10.59,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Sake bara no youni akaku}Bloom red like a rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.59,0:23:14.06,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsuyoku tsuyoku kimo wo daite}Strongly, strongly I hold you tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.06,0:23:21.02,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Tatta hitotsu kono omoi wo shinjitsu da to ieru}I can tell that only this feeling is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:25.89,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Yorokobi wo kanadeyou}Let's play the melody of pleasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:30.72,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Kagayaku mirai e}...into the bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.43,0:23:52.83,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Ah Kazoekirenai hodo tashikameaou}Let's make it sure over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.83,0:23:58.04,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Jounetu yo eien e todoke}This passion will be eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.78,0:24:02.01,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Sake bara no youni akaku}Bloom red like a rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.01,0:24:05.55,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsuyoku tsuyoku dakishimete}Strongly, strongly I hold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.55,0:24:12.44,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Tatoe nani wo ushinattemo kono ude wo hanasanai}Even if I lose everything, I won't let your arm go.
