Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.57,0:24:33.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani, you have to be true to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.22,0:24:36.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, humanity would've\Nbeen extinct by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.73,0:24:38.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}You're right, Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.30,0:24:42.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But the first time is very important.\NFor the first time, don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.06,0:24:48.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...dear?\NI'm just leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.90,0:24:50.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Are you going home, Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.51,0:24:52.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}What did you mean by\N"For the first time, don't...?"
